Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你另有看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You think otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确定  但是我认为没那么单纯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not sure. But I think there is more to than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该上班了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My shift is about start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误了你的事  很高兴又见到你  警官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't let me hold you up. It's nice seeing you again, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此  保重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Me too. Take care.
