Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问卡尔一案的进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Looking for news on Cal's case.
