Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那数据库里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What about in the database?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-卡特  -我想自己查的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Carter... - Look, I'd check myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道他们取消了我的权限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you know they pulled my access.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他们要是发现我越权查案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, they will pull mine too if they catch me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的权限也保不住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}poking around a case I'm not assigned to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  这很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  等人少点儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ok. When it clears out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  弗斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thanks, Fusco.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到号码了  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've got our number, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What do you know about this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韦恩・克鲁格  43岁  已婚  互联网业者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wayne Kruger, 43, married, Internet entrepreneur,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And what's their business?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自称提供"搜人"服务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They marketed themselves as a "People Search" service,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用户可以用来查找\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}where their users can look up old friends or relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去联系的亲友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}anyone they've fallen out of touch with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来没什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sounds harmless enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There is, however, more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这生意的重点不在帮人们取得联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Their business isn't really about reconnecting people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是收集并出售人们的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it's about collecting and selling their information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个数据掮客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's a data broker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What kind of data?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道的关于某个人的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Anything you would ever wanna know about a person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在何处居住  工作  购物  饮食\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}where they live, work, shop, eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收入多少  投票给谁  以及其他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}how much they earn, how they vote and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他把这些信息打包卖给企业  个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then he turns around and sells the information to businesses, individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}even the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这合法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is that legal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术上说  数据掮客从公开记录中获取信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Technically, data brokers get their information from public records,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是收集人们在网上泄露的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but also from the ways people reveal themselves online
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些是透明的  有些是私下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}whether they're aware or whether they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来有点像你的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sounds a little like your machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二者有本质差异\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A principle difference would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器从未泄露任何信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that the machine never reveals any of its information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给社保号码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}beyond the social security number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不怎么喜欢克鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So you're not a fan of Kruger's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为他这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}People like him are one of the reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才把机器设计成不可侵入的黑盒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I made sure the machine was impenetrable black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格刚刚进大厦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Kruger's just entered his building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在交给肖了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's in Shaw's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望让她进去的决策是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hope sending her in there was a good decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心她不够谨慎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You doubt her ability to be discreet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心她忍不住拿枪突突人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I doubt her ability to keep from shooting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm in, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格有个重要会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Kruger's got some kind of big shot meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生们  贵方能考虑与我方合作  令我们深感荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, we're thrilled that you're considering us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道里弗顿公司是零售巨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We know that Riverton is a huge retailer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要挑选潜在的数据合作方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and that you've got your pick of potential data partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也做了调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We've done our homework--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说彼得帮我们做了调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or rather Peter has done our homework, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说我们应该考虑你们公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he says you're one of the companies we should consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看过了你提供的所有信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've looked at all the information you provided,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括公司的利润  增长率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}including the company profile, growth rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾客分析数据  目标数据点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}consumer analytic statistics, and data points per target--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身份没问题吧  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Any problems with your cover, Ms. Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我打字就不会暴露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not unless someone asks me to type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇铃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A baby rattle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我剧透了惊喜  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I apologize if I spoiled the surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事  只是  我跟妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, it's all right, it's just, my wife and I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只对家里人说了  没对外公布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}haven't told anybody outside the immediate family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎么知道的  -你的葡萄酒消费\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- How did you know? - Your wine consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -从以前的一周两瓶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Excuse me? - It's dropped from two bottles a week
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降到过去的三个月几乎一瓶没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to almost nothing in the past three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的牛奶  酸奶和奶酪消费却是之前的三倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And your milk, yogurt, and cheese consumption has tripled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你购物的那家商店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The grocery store where you shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是他们"顾客忠诚项目"的会员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're members of their customer loyalty program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那项目是我们做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We created that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他们就发优惠券呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I thought they just sent out coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这种项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No. Programs like that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}are just scratching the surface of what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们"生活轨迹"真正的方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What we're really working towards here at LifeTrace
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来  所有人的需要都将被满足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}a future where every person's needs will be met
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们有所有必要的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because we have all the information necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足其需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to meet those needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以饮食习惯来预测疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Eating habits to predict diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以相配分析来消除孤身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Compatibility factors to eliminate loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其方式就是了解一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the way we do that is by getting to know someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上至生命中的大事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}from the major events of their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下至日常生活中的点点滴滴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}right down to the tiniest detail of their everyday routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全面了解一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Learning everything about a person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们得以帮助他们提升生活品质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}allows us to help them improve their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎挺吸引人  但能否问下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sounds appealing, but can I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是否有过侵犯隐私的问题呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}have you run into any issues with respect to privacy concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nothing significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有些人看我们做的事不顺眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There are always a few who take issue with what we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  现在  众所周知  科技是无法抗拒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but these days, people know, you can't fight the technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说  那些成天叫着隐私权的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And let's be honest, those crying the loudest about privacy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半藏着见不得人的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}are probably the ones trying to hide something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  巴里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's why-- uh, Barry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -因此我把我的个人资料放到了网站上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Oh, yeah. - That's why I put my own profile up on our site.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都可以看到  我没有见不得人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Anyone can look me up and see, I've got nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要个提案呈交董事会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll need to work out a proposal to present to our board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天上午可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How would tomorrow morning work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  全是他们的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, it'll be all their numbers--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这家伙出什么事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Whatever's going on with this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的生意倒是毫发无伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it sure isn't hurting his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该细查查克鲁格先生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think it's time to look a little more closely at Mr. Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些号称"没有见不得人"的人  往往都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}People who say they have nothing to hide almost always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪录上查不出什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nothing comes up on his record.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thank you for checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你现在上回白班了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I understand you're back on the day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不过我有所舍弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, but I'm giving up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走着瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻前  我想先说一声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Before we roll, I just want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的非常期待跟你一同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm really looking forward to working together and--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Laskey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  我并不想当教习警员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}one, I didn't want to be an F.T.O.,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总好过昼伏夜出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but it beats being a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Number two,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你干什么  你就干  别多问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}when I tell you to do something, just you do it, no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And number three,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰无线电  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}don't touch my radio. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡特  叫卡特就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Carter. Just Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被困在办公室算怎么一回事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How is it I got stuck being the office monkey?
