Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这笔生意一定要拿下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're right. We need this deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拿下了  得了  巴里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, we just got it. Come on, Barry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将改变一切  让我们一步登天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This changes everything. This puts us on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  海莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is it, Haley?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今晚的派对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's about the party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用您的信用卡预订\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I tried to put the restaurant deposit on your credit card
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但交易被拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but it was declined.
