Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去派对吗  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Want to go to a party, Shaw?
