Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Have you learned anything?
