Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对"生活轨迹"不利的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to suppress any bad publicity about LifeTrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆料贴子  负面新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Negative blog posts, news articles,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个联合起诉案  签了保密协议私了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Even a class action lawsuit buried in non-disclosure agreements,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上都被清干净了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All scrubbed from the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  我爱你  这是献给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sweetheart, I love you. This is for you.
