Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有见不得人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've got nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有见不得人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've got nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关掉  快关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Turn it off. Turn it off, now!
