Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  有人把克鲁格的周年纪念光盘换成了性爱录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, someone just turned Kruger's anniversary video into a sex tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, my.
