Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派对结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Party's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下越来越有意思了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just when things were getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  先是信用卡  再是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know, first his credit cards, now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在整克鲁格  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone's messing with Kruger, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要只是想羞辱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The machine wouldn't send us his number
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器是不会给出号码的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}if someone just wanted to humiliate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们得找到幕后人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, we need to find whoever's behind this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得他们对他下手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}before they come after him again.
