Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么紧张  哈罗德  我还没揍人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't sound so worried, Harold. I haven't hurt anybody...yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宽心啊  有新消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Very reassuring. You have news?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道昨晚是谁搞乱克鲁格的周年纪念了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think I know who hijacked Kruger's anniversary party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨晚酒店的监控录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Here's the restaurant's security camera footage from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人穿得像服务生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A woman dressed as a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所有的服务生以前从没见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}None of the waitstaff had seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在查看联合起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've been going through all the parties
