Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都声称私人信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All of them claim to have been victimized
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被"生活轨迹"泄露  深受其害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}when their personal information was released by LifeTrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Victimized how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份盗用  骚扰  勒索  欺诈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Identity theft, harassment, blackmail, fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至被谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Even murder.
