Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被人跟踪杀害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She lost her life to a stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人通过生活轨迹找到了她的住址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who found her home address using LifeTrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪克鲁格要把案子私了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No wonder Kruger wanted the suit buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在弗斯科警探正在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Detective Fusco is running background checks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对所有原告进行背景调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}on all of the plaintiffs as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我发现那神秘服务员了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wait, I just found our mystery waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫凯伦・米尔斯  住在皇后区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Her name is Karen Mills. She lives in Queens.
