Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.86,0:27:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搭顺风车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Bet you could use a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.65,0:27:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.83,0:28:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个你不会被那些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Somewhere you won't be attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.15,0:28:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀你的人攻击的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}by the people who are trying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.27,0:28:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.96,0:28:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  是你的唯一选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Right now, your only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的车  发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My car, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.90,0:28:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个电控元件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This electronic control unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.15,0:28:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制了车辆的内部电控元件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it overrode your car's internal E.C.U.,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.35,0:28:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让别人可以远程控制你的车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}allowing someone to control the vehicle's functions remotely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.02,0:28:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone who?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合起诉你的原告之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One of the members of that class action suit brought against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.16,0:28:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那诉讼案  我的律师达成和解了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That suit? My lawyers settled that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.77,0:28:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来并非人人满意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not to everyone's satisfaction, it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.77,0:28:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.41,0:28:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊・哈珀  被人跟踪谋杀的年轻女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Chloe Harper, the young woman killed by her stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.78,0:28:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母亲是首席原告  但是没提到她父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Her mother was lead plaintiff, but there was no mention of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚查了下他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just looked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.16,0:28:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯图・萨默斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Stu Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊没跟他姓  离婚了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Different last name than Chloe's--divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.13,0:28:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大厦里见过这个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I remember that man from your building.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.96,0:28:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是清洁工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was posing as a janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  卡尔  没来多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, Carl, hasn't been around that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.95,0:28:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为三个月前  他还是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Because until three months ago, he worked
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.60,0:29:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家航空航天研究所的电子工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}as an electrical engineer at an aerospace firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有这层背景  他有能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}With a pedigree like that, he would have the skills
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.98,0:29:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划如此周密的攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to design these sophisticated attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.23,0:29:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.89,0:29:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定在城里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He must be staying somewhere in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.91,0:29:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的人事档案  应该会有住址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His personnel file, it would have to have an address.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.96,0:29:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明早打个电话去查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can call tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.25,0:29:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.15,0:29:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你黑进了我公司的服务器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Are you hacking my building's servers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.30,0:29:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你介意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.27,0:29:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔・米勒  布鲁克林威洛斯街162号四公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Carl Miller, 162 Willow Street, apartment 4, Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.53,0:29:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在家里  就在"生活轨迹"公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He'll either be there or he'll be at LifeTrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里他有权限接入电脑系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}where he has access to the computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.85,0:29:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划下一次攻击  我去公司查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Planning his next attack. I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.99,0:29:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll hit the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.94,0:29:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧  克鲁格先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Perhaps you should rest, Mr. Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.81,0:29:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You've had quite a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么吃的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Got anything to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.46,0:30:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有煎绿茶  还有狗粮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just sencha green tea and a box of doggie treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那儿忙活的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't suppose what you're working on
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.95,0:30:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该和我无关吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}over there concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.35,0:30:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在用三角定位查找\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm trying to triangulate the location
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.72,0:30:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电梯里给你打电话的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}of the call you received in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.36,0:30:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得出声音吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did you recognize anything about the caller?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.21,0:30:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd prefer you didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.50,0:30:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别管闲事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd prefer you mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.68,0:30:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讽刺  干这行的人说出这话  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's a tad ironic, coming from a man of your profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.16,0:30:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么意思  -意思是你的职业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Meaning what? - Meaning your business
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.98,0:30:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是管别人的闲事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is minding everyone else's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.90,0:30:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作让人们生活更便捷更有质量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I do what I do to simplify and improve other people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.50,0:30:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is it that you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.75,0:31:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助他人脱离困境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We help people out of difficult situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.55,0:31:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那人是自作自受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}even situations of their own design.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.83,0:31:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那神经病想杀我  还是我的错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So it's my fault that some wacko's trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.53,0:31:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他失去了女儿  克鲁格先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The man lost his daughter, Mr. Kruger,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.78,0:31:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人用你的服务跟踪她  杀了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to a stalker who was aided by your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.25,0:31:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你觉得自己没有责任吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You feel no accountability?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.80,0:31:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这产业的年产值高达三千亿  我只是其中一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm part of a $300 billion-a-year industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.32,0:31:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息被滥用很不幸  但就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Information abuses are unfortunate, but they happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.95,0:31:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-无法阻止  -可以阻止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Can't be helped. - Oh, they can,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.41,0:31:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有权限拿到这些信息的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but only if the people who have access to the information
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.28,0:31:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意积极保护这些信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}are as interested in protecting it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.72,0:31:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同积极牟利一般\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}as they are in profiting from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.61,0:31:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看我妻子有没有打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was just checking to see if my wife had called.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.95,0:31:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认她没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I want to make sure she was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格先生  我不希望你打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Kruger, I didn't want you using the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.22,0:31:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because it might not be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.87,0:31:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你要查看信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but if you must check your messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.89,0:31:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用运营商的网络门户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we can go through your phone carrier's web portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.45,0:31:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要密码吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Need my password?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.98,0:31:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一条信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.96,0:31:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格先生  我是彼得・科利尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Kruger, Peter Collier.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.96,0:31:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和同事商量了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I spoke with my colleagues and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.95,0:31:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们同意我们再次会面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they agreed we should all sit down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.07,0:31:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你九点半前到梅菲尔德酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you could meet us at the Mayfield at 9:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.49,0:31:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能在起飞前见上一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that should give us enough time before our flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.55,0:32:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在东餐厅等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll meet you in the east dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.40,0:32:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我现在离开  还能赶上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, yes! If I leave now, I can still make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.80,0:32:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你妻子呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And what about your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.08,0:32:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在路上给她打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll call her on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.34,0:32:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格先生  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Kruger, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.81,0:32:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条信息没有"新信息"标签\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The message, it's not labeled as "New".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.73,0:32:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是有人先听过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone else must have listened to it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.67,0:32:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.55,0:32:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨默斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sommers!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.57,0:32:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他  他会在酒店那儿等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And if he's listened to it, he'll be waiting for you at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's too dangerous.
