Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.67,0:33:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.49,0:33:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里瑟先生  克鲁格跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese... Kruger's gone.
