Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.36,0:33:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在去梅菲尔德酒店的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's making his way to the Mayfield Hotel
