Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.74,0:33:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在跟踪克鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's been stalking Kruger,
