Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并最终下杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And ultimately killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去梅菲尔德酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll get over to the Mayfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.29,0:33:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  里瑟先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something else, Mr. Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.66,0:33:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格不仅是受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Kruger's not only a potential victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.87,0:33:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可能还成了行凶者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he may also now be a perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.42,0:34:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I cannot believe this is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.30,0:34:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在故意整我  你看不出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone is screwing with me. Can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.73,0:34:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm gonna fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.34,0:34:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找人吗  放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Looking for someone? Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么近我可不会射偏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I won't miss at this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.09,0:34:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什么计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So what was the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.35,0:34:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是准备在会面之前还是之后干掉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Were you gonna take me out before or after my meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.33,0:34:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没想好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hadn't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.89,0:34:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可给我造成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, you've caused me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的伤害和麻烦  萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}a great deal of pain and suffering, Mr. Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.03,0:34:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That was the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.38,0:34:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你要帮我把一切恢复原状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now, you're gonna help me get it all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.77,0:34:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格先生  你收到我的留言了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Kruger, you got my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.18,0:34:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出  什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What...happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:35:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴你问了这问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, I'm... really glad you asked.
