Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不幸  他们得搭早一班的飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, they had to catch an earlier flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.79,0:35:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们让我代为致歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They send their regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.66,0:35:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.56,0:35:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这位是萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah. This is Mr. Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.58,0:35:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们是要讨论生意合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Look, I thought we were gonna discuss our deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.00,0:35:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我给你打完电话后不久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, well, shortly after I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.43,0:35:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再次向首席执行官请示了这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We attempted to revisit the issue with our CEO,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.15,0:35:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们没法让他改变决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but we couldn't get him to reconsider his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.85,0:35:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.63,0:35:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  我以为当面谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I thought a face-to-face
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比再打电话给你要合适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}would be better than another phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.65,0:35:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.41,0:35:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Excuse me? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白我遭了多大罪才来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have no idea what I've been through to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.72,0:35:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格先生  为什么你带着枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Kruger, why do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.33,0:35:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个人羞辱了我  盗取了我的财产\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Because this man humiliated me, stole from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还想要杀死我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and even tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.19,0:35:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他的变态游戏让我们的合作告吹了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was his twisted little game that made our deal fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.47,0:35:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉他  -好了  先把枪放下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Tell him. - Okay, just, let's put down the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.57,0:36:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动手  萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't do it, Mr. Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.54,0:36:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.83,0:36:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知晓事情原委的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone who knows what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.34,0:36:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道  是他害死了我女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then you know he killed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.31,0:36:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义必须伸张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and something had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.10,0:36:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未动过你女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I never touched your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.58,0:36:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然没像那个禽兽一样亲自动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You may not have put your hands on her like that monster did,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.14,0:36:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你罪孽相同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you're just as guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.30,0:36:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.13,0:36:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的前男友找到她三次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}See, her ex-boyfriend found her three times--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.07,0:36:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三次都是通过你的"生活轨迹"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}three times, using your LifeTrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.59,0:36:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次他找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And every time he found her,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.72,0:36:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都求你的公司从网上撤下她的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we asked the company to take her information down,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.16,0:36:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们不肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and they didn't do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.70,0:36:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他又找到了我女儿  一次又一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and so he found her again, and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.19,0:36:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后杀害了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}until the last time when he killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.93,0:36:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你和你公司"什么都没做"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All because you and your company didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.27,0:37:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.66,0:37:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.34,0:37:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉可不够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sorry isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.96,0:37:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  斯图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Listen to me, Stu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.03,0:37:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你动了手  你这辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You do this, and your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.19,0:37:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.68,0:37:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.82,0:37:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Stu...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.32,0:37:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该这样纪念你的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}this isn't the way to honor your daughter's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.00,0:37:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想  克洛伊会希望你怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Think about it. What would Chloe want?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.38,0:37:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得对  为你们父女二人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You did the right thing, for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.13,0:37:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里瑟先生  我三角定位了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese, I triangulated the call
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.96,0:37:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格在电梯里接到的那通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that Kruger received in the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.73,0:37:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号现在在梅菲尔德内部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's now coming from inside the Mayfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.91,0:38:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里瑟先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Reese?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对  正义必须伸张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You were right. Something had to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.98,0:38:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才联系你  萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}which is why we reached out to you, Mr. Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.34,0:38:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你  是你给了我包裹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You--you did it. You sent me the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.17,0:38:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们给了你  为女儿伸张正义的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We sent you the means to exact justice for your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.23,0:38:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有付诸实践的勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you had the courage to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.76,0:38:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是  车祸没能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, the car crash wasn't successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.64,0:38:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只得这样即兴演出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}requiring this improvisation,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.95,0:38:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到头来总算成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but everything worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该离开了  萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You should go now, Mr. Sommers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.41,0:38:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在应该理解了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think you understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.46,0:38:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.88,0:38:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐私泄露后  你会失去什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is lost when your privacy's stripped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.58,0:39:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身份  你的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your identity, your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.30,0:39:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.17,0:39:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人身安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}security,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.96,0:39:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.51,0:39:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.87,0:39:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有千千万万像我一样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And thousands more just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.31,0:39:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不愿再沉默  而选择采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}People who have chosen action over apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.47,0:39:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新夺回被你这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to take back what men like you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和政府偷走的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and the government have stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.00,0:39:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是游戏  克鲁格先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This wasn't a game, Mr. Kruger,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.84,0:39:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}this was a lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.20,0:39:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.96,0:39:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来只想吓吓你  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were just gonna scare you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那改变不了什么  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that wouldn't change anything, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.59,0:39:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.38,0:39:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰  你中枪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}John, are you shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.70,0:40:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打在防弹衣上了  估计肋骨断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My vest caught it. Think my rib's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.45,0:40:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁格呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Kruger?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's dead, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.21,0:40:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.61,0:40:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.67,0:40:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去追科利尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I need to get to Collier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.78,0:40:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得离开这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We've got to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.44,0:40:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说得对  里瑟先生  以后再说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She's right, Mr. Reese. Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.04,0:40:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想吐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Back for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.36,0:40:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I need to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.23,0:40:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我买杯咖啡不行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Can it wait until after you buy me coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.58,0:40:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你必须带搭档才能上回白班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know you had to take a partner to get back on days,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.82,0:40:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知不知道有两个新人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but did you know that two other rookies
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.21,0:40:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是排在我之前应该跟你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}were supposed to be in this seat before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.56,0:40:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都申请重新分配了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And both requested to be reassigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.35,0:40:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要换教习警员  就提出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you want another F.T.O., just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.85,0:40:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这才是重点  我没申请重新分配\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, that's the point, I didn't ask to be reassigned,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.46,0:41:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想选择你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because I chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.70,0:41:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择我  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Chose me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.18,0:41:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警察学院时  我就听说过你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}In the academy, I heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.97,0:41:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在凶案组的事迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your work with the homicide task force
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.78,0:41:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如何推翻那些腐败警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and how you took down those corrupt cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.15,0:41:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.81,0:41:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  我也想那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Someday, that's what I want to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.61,0:41:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我抓住机会  在你手下受教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's why I jumped at the chance to train under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.00,0:41:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感觉你根本不愿意教习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I don't get the sense that you want to train anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.72,0:41:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿你甩掉我算了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}then I'd prefer it if you just cut me loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.52,0:41:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3A10  莫里斯大街和149街交汇发生一起车祸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}3-Adam-10, we got a report of a 10-53 near Morris and 149th.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.47,0:41:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到  调度中心  3A10前往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Roger, dispatch. 3-Adam-10 responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.89,0:42:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给里弗顿公司的总部打了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I made a call to Riverton's home office.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.09,0:42:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科利尔  当然是假名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Seems Collier, no doubt an alias,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.86,0:42:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没回去上班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}has not returned to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.00,0:42:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I don't think he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.50,0:42:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他四个月前开始担任顾客分析副总一职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He started four months ago as V.P. of customer analytics,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以藉此接近克鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}a position that allowed him to get close enough to Kruger
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.31,0:42:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得以见证并参与\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}so that he could both witness and participate
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.14,0:42:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉他生活的整个过程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}in the dismantling of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.02,0:42:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉克鲁格  还有跟他一样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He told Kruger there were others like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.26,0:42:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这点我相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, and I'm inclined to believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.75,0:42:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现寄给萨默斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I discovered that the anonymous packages
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.96,0:42:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他人的匿名包裹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}sent to Mr. Sommers and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.83,0:42:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经由邮政中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}came through mail-processing centers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.97,0:42:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发往全国的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}scattered all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.76,0:42:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来可以省掉包裹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Could've saved on the postage
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.95,0:42:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到机会直接爆头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and just shot him when they had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.71,0:42:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是说  这计划煞费苦心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm just saying it was an elaborate plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.53,0:42:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不仅是要杀死克鲁格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It wasn't just about killing Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.25,0:42:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要给被伤害者以报仇的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was about giving the people he hurt a chance at retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.46,0:42:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是实践一种理念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And also putting an ideology into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.60,0:42:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科利尔称杀害克鲁格是"一个教训"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Collier referred to Kruger's murder as "A lesson".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.98,0:42:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The first.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.45,0:42:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他背后的组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I fear that whatever his organization's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.09,0:42:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极目标为何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}ultimate goals may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.98,0:43:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这仅仅是开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}this could be just the beginning.

